                    <image class="weui-article__img" src="https://zsb.bupt.edu.cn/__local/C/FC/EC/9C1AB7AAF51F007491C20467E23_11A29822_12DF7.jpg?e=.jpg" mode="widthFix" style="height: 327rpx; width: 635rpx; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box" />
